In the underground of the two Azovstal steel mills, about three thousand soldiers and fighters are still hidden. The Pit-404 laboratory, again according to Escobar‚Äôs reconstructions, would be a structure dedicated to the study of chemical and biological weapons. More than three hundred military consultants would be trapped in the tunnels, officers from Germany, Canada, the United States, France, Italy, Poland, Turkey, Sweden and Greece.
